parameters.name: UT
parameters.description: Universal Time of day represented as milliseconds after 00:00:00.000

parameters.description: Density of superthermal atomic oxygen in cm**-3

parameters.name: FANG
parameters.description:
Apparent angle, in degrees, of the ion flow in the ecliptic            
       plane measured with respect to the sun
